{"tid":1704821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Mike Pence線人: 張曉明很可能被美國制裁","createTime":"2019-11-10T22:06:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T06:23:22.000Z","uid":134071,"like":232,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"5df1ec06a6fee51559544fb33d011c62445c6bc0","tid":1704821,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T22:06:56.000Z","msg":"Mark Simon-共和黨黨員， 黎智英助手， 最近更協助安排黎智英會見美國副總統Mike Pence。<br />\n<br />\nMark Simon發言, 向來比較小心謹慎 (比黎智英更小心). &nbsp;佢而家話張曉明很可能被美國制裁, 應該係<strong>首次點名</strong>.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1193549747434352641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1193549747434352641&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=dba865f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1193549747434352641&h=97866887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1193549747434352641</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/73TzrX2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F73TzrX2.jpg&h=70006687&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb85da34b1f2c14d7fc4f932a0da6610886bbac1","tid":1704821,"uid":134071,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T22:08:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20190906/china-hong-kong-protests/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fchina%2F20190906%2Fchina-hong-kong-protests%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=9c8f4cc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20190906/china-hong-kong-protests/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n其中一個引起注意的面孔是香港傳媒大亨黎智英(Jimmy Lai)的高級助手馬克&middot;西蒙(Mark Simon)，大陸對黎智英厭惡至極。<strong>西蒙曾在美國海軍服役，今年7月，他幫助安排了黎智英與副總統彭斯的見面</strong>，引發了中國的正式外交抗議。"},{"pid":"328cf86163c0a1980b8fd0a65485bf9ee55a3838","tid":1704821,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":